Package com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.settings.firewall.security.intrusion_services

Class IntrusionServicesFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.settings.firewall.security.intrusion_services.IntrusionServicesFactory
  • public class IntrusionServicesFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    IntrusionServicesFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.settings.firewall.security.intrusion_services package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
